---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = "Tax Extension Help — File by October 15, 2026 | Fiscus Max";
const description = "Filed a tax extension in April? The October 15, 2026 deadline is approaching. Fiscus Max helps families file accurately, minimize penalties, and resolve what they owe. Free consultation.";
const canonical = "https://fiscusmax.com/tax-extension";
const keywords = "tax extension deadline 2026, October 15 tax deadline, tax extension help Dallas, file tax extension return, IRS extension penalty, tax extension working families";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <head>
    <link rel="canonical" href={canonical} />
    <meta name="keywords" content={keywords} />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Tax Extension Help — File by October 15, 2026 | Fiscus Max" />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:url" content={canonical} />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  </head>

  <main class="ext-page">

    <!-- ============================================================
         SECTION 1 — HERO
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="ext-hero reveal">
      <div class="ext-hero-inner">
        <p class="ext-label ext-label--gold">Tax Extensions</p>
        <h1 class="ext-headline">
          <span class="grad-gold">Extensions Don't Eliminate What You Owe. We Help You Prepare.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="ext-sub">
          Millions of families filed for an extension this year. That bought time, not forgiveness.
          Let Fiscus Max help you file correctly, maximize your return, and avoid costly penalties
          before October 15, 2026.
        </p>
        <div class="ext-ctas">
          <a
            href="https://forms.monday.com/forms/755fc9f7b7fef79ebac688141a00bf74?r=use1"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="btn-primary"
          >Book Your Free Extension Consultation</a>
          <a href="#extension-explained" class="btn-secondary">Learn What Your Extension Means</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ============================================================
         SECTION 2 — WHAT AN EXTENSION MEANS
    ============================================================ -->
    <section id="extension-explained" class="ext-explained">
      <div class="ext-section-inner">

        <div class="ext-header reveal">
          <p class="ext-label ext-label--green">Extension Explained</p>
          <h2 class="ext-section-title">
            <span class="grad-dark">An Extension Gives You Time to File. Not Time to Pay.</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="ext-body-text reveal">
          <p>
            This is the most misunderstood thing about tax extensions. When you filed for an extension,
            the IRS gave you until October 15 to submit your return. But if you owed taxes on April 15,
            interest and penalties have been accumulating since then.
          </p>
          <p>
            The good news: there is still time to minimize the damage, get your return filed correctly,
            and potentially reduce what you owe. The worse news: every day you wait makes it more
            expensive. Fiscus Max specializes in exactly this situation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="ext-cards">

          <div class="ext-card reveal reveal-d1">
            <h3 class="ext-card-title">Extensions Are Common</h3>
            <p class="ext-card-body">
              Millions of Americans file extensions every year. It is not a red flag and it does not
              increase your audit risk. What matters is filing correctly by October 15.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="ext-card reveal reveal-d2">
            <h3 class="ext-card-title">Penalties Are Real</h3>
            <p class="ext-card-body">
              The failure-to-file penalty is 5% of unpaid taxes per month up to 25%. The sooner you
              file, the sooner those penalties stop.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="ext-card reveal reveal-d3">
            <h3 class="ext-card-title">We Handle It All</h3>
            <p class="ext-card-body">
              From calculating what you owe to filing your return to negotiating payment plans,
              Fiscus Max handles every step of the extension filing process.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>




    <!-- ============================================================
         SECTION 4 — EXTENSION FAQ
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="ext-faq">
      <div class="ext-section-inner">

        <div class="ext-header reveal">
          <p class="ext-label ext-label--green">Extension FAQ</p>
          <h2 class="ext-section-title">
            <span class="grad-dark">Questions About Your Extension</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="ext-faq-list" id="extFaqList">

          <div class="ext-faq-item reveal">
            <button class="ext-faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>What should I do if I filed a tax extension?</span>
              <svg class="ext-faq-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M4 6.5L9 11.5L14 6.5" stroke="#d6b12f" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="ext-faq-a">
              <p>If you filed a tax extension, you have until October 15, 2026 to submit your complete
              return. You should gather all your documents, calculate what you owe, and file before
              the deadline to avoid failure-to-file penalties of 5% per month.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ext-faq-item reveal">
            <button class="ext-faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>When is the tax extension deadline in 2026?</span>
              <svg class="ext-faq-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M4 6.5L9 11.5L14 6.5" stroke="#d6b12f" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="ext-faq-a">
              <p>The 2026 tax extension deadline is October 15, 2026. This applies to individuals who
              filed Form 4868 by April 15, 2026.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ext-faq-item reveal">
            <button class="ext-faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Does a tax extension mean I don't have to pay?</span>
              <svg class="ext-faq-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M4 6.5L9 11.5L14 6.5" stroke="#d6b12f" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="ext-faq-a">
              <p>No. A tax extension gives you more time to file your return but does not extend the
              time to pay taxes owed. Interest and penalties on unpaid taxes began accruing on April 15.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ext-faq-item reveal">
            <button class="ext-faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Can I get help filing my tax extension return?</span>
              <svg class="ext-faq-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M4 6.5L9 11.5L14 6.5" stroke="#d6b12f" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="ext-faq-a">
              <p>Yes. Tax professionals like Fiscus Max specialize in helping individuals and families
              file extension returns accurately, minimize penalties, and set up payment plans when
              needed. Consultations are free.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ============================================================
         SECTION 5 — BLOG POST PREVIEW
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="ext-blog reveal">
      <div class="ext-blog-inner">
        <p class="ext-label ext-label--gold">Tax Extension Resources</p>
        <h2 class="ext-blog-title">
          <span class="grad-gold">Filed a Tax Extension? Here's Everything You Need to Do Before October 15</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="ext-blog-body">
          Understanding what your extension means is the first step. Knowing exactly what to do next
          is what Fiscus Max is here for. Read our complete guide to extension filing and learn how
          to minimize penalties, calculate what you owe, and file correctly before the deadline.
        </p>
        <a href="/resources/blog/tax-extension-october-deadline" class="btn-primary">Read the Full Guide</a>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ============================================================
         SECTION 6 — FINAL CTA
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="ext-final-cta reveal">
      <div class="ext-final-inner">
        <p class="ext-label ext-label--gold">Before You Go</p>
        <h2 class="ext-final-title">
          <span class="grad-gold">October 15 Is Closer Than You Think.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="ext-final-body">
          Every day without filing adds interest and penalties to what you owe. Your first consultation
          is free, takes less than 10 minutes, and could save your family hundreds. Do not wait.
        </p>
        <div class="ext-contact-pill">
          469-966-9071 &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; consult@fiscusmax.com &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Mon–Sun 9am–9pm
        </div>
        <a
          href="https://forms.monday.com/forms/755fc9f7b7fef79ebac688141a00bf74?r=use1"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn-primary ext-final-btn"
        >Book Your Free Extension Consultation Now</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

</BaseLayout>


<script>
  // ============================================================
  // SCROLL REVEAL
  // ============================================================
  const revealEls = document.querySelectorAll('.ext-page .reveal');
  const extRevealObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) entry.target.classList.add('visible');
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.1, rootMargin: '0px 0px -40px 0px' });
  revealEls.forEach(el => extRevealObserver.observe(el));

  // ============================================================
  // FAQ ACCORDION
  // ============================================================
  const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll('.ext-faq-item');
  faqItems.forEach(item => {
    const btn = item.querySelector('.ext-faq-q');
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');
      faqItems.forEach(i => {
        i.classList.remove('open');
        i.querySelector('.ext-faq-q').setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
      });
      if (!isOpen) {
        item.classList.add('open');
        btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');
      }
    });
  });
</script>


<style>
  .ext-page {
    background: #f8f4e5;
  }

  /* ==========================================================
     SECTION 1 — HERO
  ========================================================== */
  .ext-hero {
    background: #211057;
    padding: 180px 24px 100px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ext-hero-inner {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ext-label {
    font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 400;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .ext-label--gold { color: #d6b12f; }
  .ext-label--green { color: #114b1c; }

  .ext-headline {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 45px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .ext-sub {
    font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(248, 244, 229, 0.85);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
  }

  .ext-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* ==========================================================
     SECTION 2 — EXTENSION EXPLAINED
  ========================================================== */
  .ext-explained {
    background: #f8f4e5;
    padding: 80px 24px;
  }

  .ext-section-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ext-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .ext-section-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .ext-body-text {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto 56px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ext-body-text p {
    font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #114b1c;
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .ext-body-text p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* Cards */
  .ext-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .ext-card {
    background: #f8f4e5;
    border: 1.5px solid #114b1c;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px;
    transition: border-color 0.28s ease, transform 0.28s ease, box-shadow 0.28s ease;
  }

  .ext-card:hover {
    border-color: #d6b12f;
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(214, 177, 47, 0.18);
  }

  .ext-card-title {
    font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #114b1c;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ext-card-body {
    font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(17, 75, 28, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  /* ==========================================================
     SECTION 3 — STATS BAR
  ========================================================== */
  .ext-stats {
    background: #211057;
    padding: 48px 24px;
  }

  .ext-stats-inner {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .ext-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 0 48px;
  }

  .ext-stat-num {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .ext-stat-label {
    font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 400;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: rgba(248, 244, 229, 0.65);
  }

  .ext-stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(214, 177, 47, 0.2);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ==========================================================
     SECTION 4 — FAQ
  ========================================================== */
  .ext-faq {
    background: #f8f4e5;
    padding: 80px 24px;
  }

  .ext-faq-list {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ext-faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(17, 75, 28, 0.15);
  }

  .ext-faq-item:first-child {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(17, 75, 28, 0.15);
  }

  .ext-faq-q {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    padding: 22px 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: left;
    font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #114b1c;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .ext-faq-arrow {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform 0.28s ease;
  }

  .ext-faq-item.open .ext-faq-arrow {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .ext-faq-a {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: 0fr;
    transition: grid-template-rows 0.32s ease;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ext-faq-item.open .ext-faq-a {
    grid-template-rows: 1fr;
  }

  .ext-faq-a p {
    font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(17, 75, 28, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.8;
    padding-bottom: 22px;
    min-height: 0;
  }

  /* ==========================================================
     SECTION 5 — BLOG PREVIEW
  ========================================================== */
  .ext-blog {
    background: #114b1c;
    padding: 80px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ext-blog-inner {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ext-blog-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .ext-blog-body {
    font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(248, 244, 229, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.9;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 36px;
  }

  /* ==========================================================
     SECTION 6 — FINAL CTA
  ========================================================== */
  .ext-final-cta {
    background: #211057;
    padding: 80px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ext-final-inner {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ext-final-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .ext-final-body {
    font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(248, 244, 229, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .ext-contact-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d6b12f, #b5923b);
    color: #0a2910;
    font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 400;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .ext-final-btn {
    font-size: 17px;
    padding: 16px 36px;
  }

  /* ==========================================================
     RESPONSIVE
  ========================================================== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ext-hero { padding: 150px 20px 72px; }
    .ext-explained, .ext-faq, .ext-blog, .ext-final-cta { padding: 60px 20px; }
    .ext-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ext-stats-inner { gap: 32px; }
    .ext-stat { padding: 0 24px; }
    .ext-stat-divider { width: 40px; height: 1px; }
    .ext-sub { font-size: 17px; }
    .ext-ctas { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .ext-stat-divider { display: none; }
    .ext-stats-inner { gap: 24px; }
  }
</style>
